dct.coverage_comparison = Mock_coverage().coverage_comparison
hl_covers = {'low': 20, 'high': 30}
hl_poss = {'low': 1, 'high': 2}
term = {'start': 2, 'end': 4}
covers = [100, 30, 23, 21, 21]
term_covers = []
args = self.mock_args.mock()
args.fuzzy = 1
args.decrease = 0.5
dct.coverage2term(covers, term, hl_covers, hl_poss, '+', term_covers,
    'track_1', args, 0, 4, 'frag')
self.assertDictEqual(term_covers[0], {'diff': 70, 'track': 'track_1',
    'type': 'frag', 'high': 100, 'low': 30, 'detect': 'True'})
